{
 "name": "RPlog_Shopping_with_Sith",
 "title": "Shopping with Sith",
 "summary": "On Imperial Way in the domed city of Selene, the newly appointed Moff Elana Tracer finishes a shopping trip just as several notable figures converge on her. Johanna Damion, sister to the Imperator Darth Malign and reluctantly shadowed by her mutant Wookiee minder Sentinel, stops to congratulate her former swooping idol Tracer, while the Sith Lord Vassily Korolov and the smarmy doctor Basca Starker each approach with their own agendas. Korolov needles the nervous Tracer and trades barbed pleasantries with Johanna before excusing himself, promising his aide will contact her staff for talks. When Basca's flippant manner grates on everyone, Johanna sharply insists he show the Moff respect; he apologizes, introduces himself as the doctor who fought the Sariphage plague on Caspar, and falls into a more civil conversation with Tracer about the system's future.",
